Package ohos.ai.cv.common

Class VisionConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.ai.cv.common.VisionConfiguration
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DocRefineConfiguration, SisrConfiguration, TextConfiguration, TxtImageSuperResolutionConfiguration

    public class VisionConfiguration
extends Object
    Defines common configurations for CV abilities.

    This class is used to set configuration parameters for running CV abilities, including the mode-in, mode-out, and application type.

    Since:
    1
